ZH: 我明白你的意思。
EN: I understand what you mean.

ZH: 请你明白我们的立场。
EN: Please understand our position.

ZH: 我们需要明白这个问题的重要性。
EN: We need to understand the importance of this issue.

ZH: 他应该明白自己的责任。
EN: He should understand his responsibility.

ZH: 你必须明白这些规则。
EN: You must understand these rules.

ZH: 我明白你的感受。
EN: I understand your feelings.

ZH: 请你明白我的苦衷。
EN: Please understand my difficulties.

ZH: 他们似乎完全明白了我的意图。
EN: They seem to completely understand my intentions.

ZH: 她终于明白了自己的错误。
EN: She finally understood her mistakes.

ZH: 请你明白这只是我的建议。
EN: Please understand that this is just my suggestion.

ZH: 希望他们能够明白我们的立场。
EN: I hope they can understand our position.

ZH: 他们需要明白这个决定的重要性。
EN: They need to understand the importance of this decision.

ZH: 请尽量明白我的意图。
EN: Please try to understand my intentions.

ZH: 他们需要明白局势的严重性。
EN: They need to understand the seriousness of the situation.

ZH: 希望你能够明白这个难题。
EN: I hope you can understand this difficult problem.

ZH: 请你明白这是为了大家的利益。
EN: Please understand that this is for everyone's benefit.

ZH: 我们必须明白时机的重要性。
EN: We must understand the importance of timing.

ZH: 希望他们终将明白这个真相。
EN: I hope they will eventually understand the truth.

ZH: 他们似乎不愿意明白我的观点。
EN: They seem unwilling to understand my point of view.

ZH: 请你明白这个问题的复杂性。
EN: Please understand the complexity of this issue.
